{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" = ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GSourceFuncsPrepareFunc","text":"GSourceFuncsPrepareFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Called before all the file descriptors are polled. If the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"source can determine that it is ready here (without waiting for the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"results of the poll call) it should return "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". It can also return"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a "},{"code":"timeout","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" value which should be the maximum timeout (in milliseconds)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which should be passed to the poll call. The actual timeout used will","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"be ","type":"text"},{"code":"-1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if all sources returned "},{"code":"-1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", or it will be the minimum of all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"code":"timeout","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" values returned which were greater than or equal to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If the prepare function returns a timeout and the source also has a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ready time set, then the lower of the two will be used.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since 2.36 this may be "},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", in which case the effect is as if the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"function always returns ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FALSE"},{"text":" with a timeout of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-1"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checks the source for readiness."}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","roleHeading":"Type Alias","externalID":"s:4GLib22SourceFuncsPrepareFunca","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"fragments":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc"}],"symbolKind":"typealias","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/sourcefuncspreparefunc"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceFuncsPrepareFunc"},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/SourceFuncsPrepareFunc":{"title":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/sourcefuncspreparefunc","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checks the source for readiness."}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib","kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","abstract":[],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","role":"collection"}}}